After winning the title in his opponentâ€™s home territory of Germany earlier this year, Murtazaliev (23-0, 17 KOs) made a statement by dropping Tszyu (24-2, 17 KOs) early and often on his way to the dominant stoppage. The first knockdown came in round two with a strong counter left hook sending Tszyu to the canvas. Tszyu showed the incredible grit thatâ€™s made him a superstar in his native Australia to rise to his feet, but was ultimately sent back to the ground two more times in the round. We just worked on these combinations all the time and when the fight came, it was automatic,â€ said Murtazaliev. â€œWe worked for 10 weeks on those punches that hurt him. We created opportunities and we believed that we could win this fight.â€ Continuing to press forward and look for moments in round three, Murtazaliev landed another vicious counter left hand that scored him his fourth knockdown in less than three rounds. While Tszyu continued to battle back, the onslaught from Murtazaliev proved to be too much as Tszyuâ€™s corner threw in the towel, ending the fight 1:55 into the round. When I landed that first big shot, I knew how hard it was,â€ said Murtazaliev. â€œTszyu is a real warrior and I hope one day we can work together and spar and help each other to grow. Every time I step into the ring I leave it all in there,â€ said Tszyu. â€œThings didn't go to plan and the better man won tonight. No excuses. After the first shot, things started not going according to plan. That's part of boxing, you get hit and reactions get slower. description: Wild Life: Episode 1 - ANYTHING COULD HAPPEN!Welcome to WILD LIFE the next season in the Wild Life series. This time, there will be a different twist that affects the game every session/episode (only one person episode). The twists may or may not present some danger to the participants. This season, we have 6 lives. 4-6 Lives you have a dark green name. 3 lives you have a lime green name. 2 lives you have a yellow name and on your last and final life, you turn hostile and red. title: JJ Reddick Delivered A Coaching MASTERCLASS On Opening Night
tags: [none]
description: RateGame Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rategamemobile&pcampaignid=web_shareRateGame iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id6477869711?pt=126905374&ct=HeatCheckRegSzn24-25&mt=8Opening night was a real spectacle and despite all the hype being around the father and son duo, I was most intrigued by JJ Reddick and his offensive tricks.First play of the game you already see the motion in the offense, with Lebron setting a good screen on the wing the diving hard to the basket, which forces Gobert to rotate, and from there the ball movement to the corner, and a swing to Hachimuraâ€¦And the very next play Rui explodedâ€¦His phenomenal start was further emphasized on the defensive end. Watch the activity helping on the Randle back down and then the great recoveryâ€¦The Lakers defense led to another Lebron bucket and this time, it was a way better finish.But despite the highlights, and the crowd going crazy, Minnesota managed to keep up with the Lakers, led by Anthony Edwards with 8 first quarter points, and he showed the crowd some of his flash.Second quarter comes along and you see the 2-3 zone that the Wolves are in, but check out Dâ€™Angelo Russel literally sneaking his way to the middle of the zone, forcing a response from the back line, and delivering a fantastic pass to the cutting Hayes for the dunk.Then, moments later Reddick runs horns with the sharpshooter Knecht on the weak side. And watch him take off setting a back screen for Lebron, clearing out the perimeter for a handoff and a screen for himself. Reid has to come out and contest it, so this split second of help allows Hayes to cut inside, and the great pass by Knecht for the throwdown.The next possession itâ€™s almost the exact same thing with Dalton screening again for Lebron of the ball and sprinting out around the Jackson Hayes pick and this time, the defender is trailing him so he can fire away from downtownâ€¦These terrific offensive possessions would spark a 27-6 run by the Lakers, sending the arena into delirium.And this built enough of a cushion for Bronny to come into the game in a historic moment.And he had his 1 chance for a bucketâ€¦He couldnâ€™t hit this one for the fans, but senior sure gave them something to cheer for.The Lakers are up by 13 at the half, and JJ starts off the second half with some more motion into the offense.Austin Reeves runs across 2 picks on the so-called Iverson cut, and Lebron follows, setting a hybrid between a screen and a slip, which creates hesitation for the defense, and at this moment he is obviously open for the bounce pass, which creates a 2 on 1 between him AD and Gobert. So itâ€™s a perfect execution as we let it roll, for a beautiful alley oop dunk.Thing is, it was mostly AD for the Lakers in this quarter. On both ends of the court.And despite a terrific quarter of 13 points and 5 rebounds, Minnesota started to get into a rhythm and went on a mini run towards the end.This gave me hope for an exciting finish but maaan, Anthony Davis went god mode in the 4th and he was not going to let the Lakers lose on opening night.36 points, 16 rebounds, 4 assists and 3 blocks a blockbuster performance from AD.I gave this game a 6.6 on Rate Game which was obviously lower than what Lakers fans rated it.And if youâ€™re new around here, Rate Game is an app that Iâ€™m a part of, made for the real fans of the game.In a world polluted by betting and gambling, Rate Game is a pure diary where you keep track of what games you watched and which ones were the best. I watch a ton of games every season so this is great for me to look back on. We now have a hide scores feature so you can only see the ratings and decide which game to watch in the morning based on the scores. This feature is gamechanger.Iâ€™m on here every night so join me to see what Iâ€™m watching and to post what you saw . The new design is sick, and we now have all the major US sports along with the Premier League Soccer and NCAA action. Click the link in the description for iOS or Android.Moving on to ring night in Boston where it was all smiles before the game. I, on the other hand, had high hopes for my brand new Knicks. Boy I had no idea what I was in for.First play of the game we got the high screen for Tatum and Towns is not willing to commit all the way and risk getting blown by. So JT gets a practice shot and he swishes it.The high big men screens would be the Knicks nemesis, as we see another one here and the great maneuver by Kornet to switch the side at the last second, fooling the defender and opening up another shot for Tatum for another three.JT said during preseason that he was tinkering with his shot, and some bozo made a youtube video doubting him. Of course then he responds with a 15 point first quarter going 4 for 6 from downtown. This opened up a barrage of threes by the Celtics, collectively going 10 for 17 from long range in the opening period alone.

This Valentineâ€™s Day, OscarÂ® winner Ke Huy Quan (Everything Everywhere All at Once, Loki) rockets into his first major leading man role as an unlikely hero, a seemingly mild-mannered realtor with a dark secret that he is desperate to leave behind. Spoiler alert: He wonâ€™t. From 87Northâ€”producers of the groundbreaking action films Nobody, Violent Night, Bullet Train, Atomic Blonde and The Fall Guyâ€”comes a visceral, high-octane story of wrath and revenge.  Quan stars as Marvin Gable, a realtor working the Milwaukee suburbs, where â€˜For Saleâ€™ signs bloom. Gable receives a crimson envelope from Rose (OscarÂ® winner Ariana DeBose; West Side Story, Argylle), a former partner-in-crime that he had left for dead. Sheâ€™s not happy. Now, Marvin is thrust back into a world of ruthless hitmen, filled with double-crosses and open houses turned into deadly warzones. Guy Danella (Violent Night) is also producing. The executive producer is Ben Ormand.  Making his feature film directing debut on Love Hurts is acclaimed veteran stunt coordinator and fight coordinator JoJo Eusebio, whose credits include some of the greatest action films of the past decade including Black Panther, The Avengers, the John Wick films, The Matrix Resurrections, Violent Night, The Fall Guy and Deadpool 2. description: For the special finale episode, I'll be discussing the ins and outs of the creation of this channel. Of course, this one's not an actual game, but on my Japanese channel this category is called Project Conceptsâ€”so it's not strictly restricted to games, after all!---Though my final video's been released, the channel itself won't be going anywhere. Whatever the case, I hope our paths cross again soon!

title: It Turns Out, Hybrids Are Really Hard On Engines
tags: [none]
description: Hybrid vehicles are uniquely challenging due to the frequent engine start/stops, as well as lower overall engine temperatures, which can lead to water and fuel dilution.Sponsored by Mobil 1 â€“ https://www.mobil.com/en/lubricants/ Hybrid vehicles are a great solution to improving fuel economy, but they have their own unique challenges. Because hybrid engines start & stop frequently, this often results in lower engine temperatures, which in turn can create issues with water and fuel dilution. Frequent start/stops, water, and fuel, can all create problems that exacerbate engine wear. To combat this, Mobil 1 has developed Mobil 1 hybrid, a full synthetic motor oil that is designed to meet the challenges that hybrid vehicles place on engines. This video will focus on three main subjects: how hybrids work, why hybrids are hard on engines, and what solutions exist to combat these challenges. Don't forget to check out my other pages below! Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/engineeringexplained Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/engineeringexplained EE Extra: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsrY4q8xGPJQbQ8HPQZn6iA
channel_description: How do cars work? It's a simple question, without a simple answer. That's what this channel is for! You could search the web endlessly for consumable information, or you can watch my simple to understand videos. I'm a graduated mechanical engineer with a passion for cars, and my goal is to help other people passionate about cars learn how they work. description: What if someone you loved became something else? #WolfManMovie only in theaters January 17.---From Blumhouse and visionary writer-director Leigh Whannell, the creators of the chilling modern monster tale The Invisible Man, comes a terrifying new lupine nightmare: Wolf Man. Golden Globe nominee Christopher Abbott (Poor Things, It Comes at Night) stars as Blake, a San Francisco husband and father, who inherits his remote childhood home in rural Oregon after his own father vanishes and is presumed dead. With his marriage to his high-powered wife, Charlotte (Emmy winner Julia Garner; Ozark, Inventing Anna), fraying, Blake persuades Charlotte to take a break from the city and visit the property with their young daughter, Ginger (Matlida Firth; Hullraisers, Coma).But as the family approaches the farmhouse in the dead of night, theyâ€™re attacked by an unseen animal and, in a desperate escape, barricade themselves inside the home as the creature prowls the perimeter. As the night stretches on, however, Blake begins to behave strangely, transforming into something unrecognizable, and Charlotte will be forced to decide whether the terror within their house is more lethal than the danger without. The film co-stars Sam Jaeger (The Handmaidâ€™s Tale), Ben Prendergast (The Sojourn Audio Drama) and Benedict Hardie (The Invisible Man). Wolf Man is directed by Whannell, whose previous films with Blumhouse include The Invisible Man, Upgrade and Insidious: Chapter 3. The screenplay is written by Leigh Whannell & Corbett Tuck, Lauren Schuker Blum & Rebecca Angelo (Dumb Money). The film is produced by Blumhouse founder and CEO Jason Blum and is executive produced by Ryan Gosling, Ken Kao, Bea Sequeira, Mel Turner and Leigh Whannell. Wolf Man is a Blumhouse and Motel Movies production. description: The Simsâ„¢ 4 Life & Death Expansion Pack* arrives Oct 31 and is available for pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack  Order now through Dec 12 for the Macabre Mementos Digital Content**; the Lasting Legacy Family Portrait, Mournful Melodies Music Box, and Plumed Elegance Mask.Peel back the veil: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack  Sims can collect Bucket List goals and earn rewards for completing them â€“ but don't worry if they can't! If a Sim dies with Unfinished Business they can still live(?) their dreams as a Ghost, and still earn rewards. The ultimate reward for completing Bucket Lists and Unfinished Business is Rebirth.For Sims who want to live life on the dark side there are two new careers; an off-screen Mortician career and an active Reaper career which will let you go work for Grim at his secret office as well as travel to reap souls.There's a lot of eerie fun to get into off the clock as well. Explore Crypts, build your Thanatlogy skill, collect tarot cards, and even adopt a Pet Crow.Death affects different Sims in different ways. Create fully custom Grieving Rituals and decorate Caskets and Gravesites according to the wishes of the departed Sim or their loved ones. There are 4 types of grief which Sims may experience depending on their personalities and their relationship to the deceased.Sims can also prepare for their own deaths in life by creating Wills and deciding who to pass on Heirlooms, assets, and children should they pass away.The journey doesn't end with death. Sims can continue on as Ghosts and even learn new supernatural powers. Ghosts who are helpful while haunting will earn Goodwill essence while Ghosts who think it's fun to be frightening will earn Fear essence. Both essences can be sold for Simoleans.Embrace the Macabre (one of 3 new traits!) in Life & Death.Available October 31 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStationÂ®4, and PlayStationÂ®5. Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.**Conditions and restrictions apply. See https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack
